    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Kehniſch eezeble\nBenajn Jojada Dehlu winna\nWeetâ pahr to Karra-Spehku /\nun to Preesteri Zadaku eezeble\ntas Kehniſch Abjatara Weetâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz nosuhtija tas Keh-\nniſch / un likke Simeju aizi-\nnaht/ un fazzija us to: Darrajs\nweenu Nammu Jerusaleme/ un\ndsihwo tur/ un ne iseij no tur-\nrenes ne kur/"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo kurrâ Deenâ tu us\nahru eefi/ un pahr to Uppi Kih-\ndranu eefi/ tad finni teefcham/\nka tu teefcham nomirſi/ taws At-\nfins lai paleek us tawu Galwu."
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Simejus us\nto Kehniſu : Tas irr labs\nWahrds/ ka mans Kungs tas\nKehniſch irr runnajs/ ta darrihs\ntaws Kalps. Ta dsihwoja Si-\nmejus Jerusaleme ilgu Laiku."
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pehz trim Gaddeim\ntas notikabs/ ka Sinejum di-\nwi Kalpi aisbehdſe/pee AkifaMa-\neka Dehla ta Kehnixa no Gat-\ntas. Un Simejum tappe fluddi-\nabts un faazzihts: Rangi/ tawi\nKalpi irr Gatta."
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Simejus/un\napſedloja fawn Ehseli / un gahje\nus Gattu pee Akisu fawus Kal-\npus mekleht. Un ta nogahje Si-\nmejus/ un atwedde tawus Kal-\npus no Gattas."
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad tappe Salamanam\nfluddinahts/ ka Simejus bija no"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jerusalemes us Gattu gahjis/\nnn atkat pahrgahjis."
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija tas Keh-\nniſch/ un likke Simeju aizinaht/\nun fazzija us to: Neggi es to\nKUNGU minnedams tew efmu\npeekohdinajs/ un prett tew Leczt-\nbu dewis/ fazzidams: Kurra\nDeenâ tu iseefi / un jebkahda\nWeetâ staigati / tad finni tee-\nscham/ ka tu teefcham nomirſi?\nun tu fazziji us man: Es efmu\nlabbu Wahrdn dsirdejs."
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kapehz tad tu ne efi ta\nKUNGA Swehreschann tur-\nrejs/ un to Baufibu/ ko es pahr\ntew patvehlejs?"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wehl fazzija tas Kehniſch\nus Simeju: Tu finni wiſtu to\nLannu/ ko tawa Sirde apsin-\nnahs/ ko tu mannam Tehwam\nDahwidam darrijs / tapehz iru\ntas KUNGS tawu Blehdibu liž-\nzis atkat us tawu Galivu nahkt."
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Kehniſch Sa-\nlamans irr fwehfihfs/un Dahwi-\nda Gohda-Krehſlis buhs pastah-\nwigs preekich ta KUNGA ninh-\nschigi."
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Kehniſch patveh-\nleja Benajum Jojada Dehlan\ntas isgahje/ un kawe winnu/ ka\ntas nomirre. Ta ktuu ta Wa-\nstiba apſtiprinata zaur Salama-\nna Rohkn."
    }
  ],
